\lim_{x \to 0} \frac{\sin(5x)}{\sin(4x)}
\lim_{x \to 0}\frac{\sin(x)}{x}=1
=\lim_{x \to 0} \frac{\frac{5\sin(5x)}{5x}}{\frac{4\sin(4x)}{4x}}
=\frac{5}{4}\lim_{x \to 0} \frac{\frac{\sin(5x)}{5x}}{\frac{\sin(4x)}{4x}}
=\frac{5}{4}\cdot\frac{1}{1}
L=\frac{5}{4}
